{
  "stem": "24364.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And since we had quite a few married couples, it was really difficult for them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it is still thought today that it was really unnecessary hardship which was put upon us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was-- since it was changed eventually, it could have been changed quite at the beginning and people wouldn't have to have suffered.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had a commander who was, I think, a little bit sadistic.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so he tried to do certain things which were not right, like after people complained about the family-- I mean, it didn't bother me.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was too young and I was really not interested in family life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But it bothered mainly the married couples.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And since the commander was begged and-- and-- and pleaded with to do something about it, finally he decided to make one change, which I thought was awful.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They-- in the-- in the recreation grounds, they put up tents.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so three times a week when you went there for the two hours, so you could enter the tent and do your job and-- and sort of be there for half an hour, then change course, somebody else came in.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was awful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I'll never forget that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was  really awful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There were some families who had kids, small kids.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So the kids were sitting in front of the tent, watching their parents go in and come out again.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That was really terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But after about two years, or a year and-- I think about a year and a half, it was permitted for the married women to go to the men's camp at-- I think it started out with 11:00 in the morning and come back home at 6:00 at night.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And later on, it was changed to 9:00 in the morning until 9:00 at night.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
